  "description": "<p>\n\t<img src=\"http://news.bbcimg.co.uk/media/images/80019000/jpg/_80019626_black-fridya.jpg\" style=\"height: 281px; width: 500px;\" /></p>\n<p>\n\t<a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p764823\" title=\"点击获得更好的阅读体验\"><img src=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/2009/images/rss_video.gif\" /></a></p>\n<p>\n\tWe're shown pictures of crowds responding with apparently exponential <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/panic\" target=\"_blank\">panic</a>, if not violence, to pop-up sales, <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/clearance\" target=\"_blank\">clearance</a> sales, spring sales, end of season sales, and <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/manic\" target=\"_blank\">Manic</a>Monday and Black Friday.</p>\n<p>\n\tThe American import, Black Friday, is a kind of purchasing <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/orgy\" target=\"_blank\">orgy</a> which follows Thanksgiving Thursday - once a holiday about gratitude and sharing which has now morphed into a festival of over-eating, discovering you only like your family when they're not around and preparing to hate them all over again at Christmas. Last year's Thanksgiving Race in Cincinnati - usually a good-humoured <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/charitable\" target=\"_blank\">charitable</a> fun run - was marred by <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/discourtesy\" target=\"_blank\">discourtesy</a>. Snacks and drinks offered to finishing runners were grabbed by the armful, if not the boxful, and young volunteers were frightened and verbally abused. There was none of the usual surplus left for the local food bank. Observers wondered where this violent drive to consume had come from - it didn't seem to be about hunger, more the fear of hunger.</p>\n<p>\n\tAs whole sections of first world societies, of British society, realise that warm clothes for their kids, or groceries have become <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/aspirational\" target=\"_blank\">aspirational</a> - does an <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/ambient\" target=\"_blank\">ambient</a> anxiety make some of us greedier? Do we look at images of happy people with happy things and feel we need more material insulation to keep away the cold? That doesn't sound like happiness.&nbsp;</p>\n<p>\n\t<span>声明：音视频均来自互联网链接，仅供学习使用。本网站自身不存储、控制、修改被链接的内容。&ldquo;沪江</span><a>英语</a><span>&rdquo;高度重视知识产权保护。当如发现本网站发布的信息包含有侵犯其著作权的链接内容时，请联系我们，我们将依法采取措施移除相关内容或屏蔽相关链接。&gt;&gt;<a href=\"http://class.hujiang.com/course/52569?source=16553\" style=\"text-decoration: none; color: rgb(0,90,148);\" target=\"_blank\">零基础直达流利生活口语班</a>&lt;&lt;</span></p>\n<br /><center><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p764823/#relate_articles\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_chat.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p764823\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_digg.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a></center><h3 style=\"margin: 10px;\">本周最热文章</h3><ul style=\"margin: 5px 0;\"><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p763937/\">新一轮寒潮来袭 12个取暖小诀窍来帮你</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p764989/\">芭比娃娃出新款了：新造型更加接地气</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p763903/\">改变从小事开始：9个可以做到的小决心</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p762368/\">圆滚滚的问候：美国熊猫宝宝的首次亮相</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p763700/\">美高校评选年度最讨厌词汇：2016年别再用啦</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p764895/\">猴年来啦！这些猴子短语你都会说吗</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p764964/\">挪威20岁女孩称自己是只喵只是被困于人身……</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p765087/\">职场阅人术：不